ovpn_file.file:
client
dev tun
proto tcp
auth-user-pass
remote www.google.com.sg.newage888.xyz:110@mydigiapp.digi.com.my
http-proxy www.google.com.sg.newage888.xyz 8080
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Host: mydigiapp.digi.com.my
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER X-Online-Host: mydigiapp.digi.com.my
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Keep-Alive mydigiapp.digi.com.my
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Payload split
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Request-Method Head
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Injection-Method Front-Inject
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Query-Method Back-Query
http-proxy-option VERSION 1.1
keepalive 10 30
redirect-gateway local def1
dhcp-option DNS 1.1.1.1
dhcp-option DNS 1.0.0.1
dhcp-option DOMAIN google.com.my
dhcp-option DOMAIN m.google.com.my
persist-key
persist-tun
pull
resolv-retry infinite
nobind
user nobody
comp-lzo
remote-cert-tls server
verb 3
mute 20
connect-retry 5 5
cipher none
auth none
